{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, a significant number of startups have been created, with core developers often being ex-employees of large tech companies.",
    "For instance, Anthropic was founded in 2021 by senior members of OpenAI and Mistral AI is a French startup built by former members of Google DeepMind.",
    "Table 2 summarizes some of the most well-known models, along with their parameters count and context window size.",
    "Note that there are many other capable models and a more comprehensive overview is beyond the scope of this paper.",
    "Parameter count is correlated with the learning, generalization, and language understanding capabilities and hence a measure of the model's capacity and capabilities."
  ]
}